  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t我2016年写的，原文：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9mcmVlb3oub3JnL2liYnMvdGhyZWFkLTEyNTkyOTAtMS0xLmh0bWw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://freeoz.org/ibbs/thread-1259290-1-1.html\">https://freeoz.org/ibbs/thread-1259290-1-1.html</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9maWxlcy5jYXRib3gubW9lL3BvaWY0bD93aWR0aD02NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTczOA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://files.catbox.moe/poif4l?width=650&amp;height=738\"><img alt=\"https://files.catbox.moe/poif4l?width=650&amp;height=738\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/poif4l?width=650&amp;height=738\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n估计<b>泽东窑子</b>要走红西方反华各国，VIP顾客多为西方白左白右政客类，地下低档廉室内则充斥贱货五毛党狗吃领救济的窜美赖澳爱国人士无限怀念土匪祖国器官思乡情切每逢性起急赴主席窑子大爽一番翻云覆雨复习唤醒党狗奴才淫欲交配本能。<br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\">乱世笑林</a></b><br/>\n<b><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/92868\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/92868\">悉尼中领馆五毛处品葱科2026年工作会议纪实</a></b> </div>",
